body:
## Description
Define complete API contracts for REST endpoints and gRPC services with OpenAPI and Protobuf specifications.

## Tasks
- [ ] Create OpenAPI 3.0 specification for REST API
- [ ] Define authentication endpoints (OAuth 2.0/OIDC)
- [ ] Define user management endpoints
- [ ] Define game lobby endpoints
- [ ] Define game action endpoints
- [ ] Create .proto files for gRPC services
- [ ] Define real-time event messages
- [ ] Document request/response models
- [ ] Define error response standards
- [ ] Create Postman/Insomnia collection
- [ ] Generate API documentation (Swagger UI)
- [ ] Add request/response examples

## REST API Endpoints

### Authentication
- POST `/api/auth/register` - Register new user
- POST `/api/auth/login` - Login with credentials
- POST `/api/auth/refresh` - Refresh access token
- POST `/api/auth/logout` - Logout
- GET `/api/auth/user` - Get current user

### Game Lobby
- GET `/api/games` - List available games
- POST `/api/games` - Create new game
- GET `/api/games/{id}` - Get game details
- POST `/api/games/{id}/join` - Join game
- POST `/api/games/{id}/leave` - Leave game
- DELETE `/api/games/{id}` - Cancel game (creator only)

### Game Actions
- POST `/api/games/{id}/start` - Start game
- POST `/api/games/{id}/rounds/current/trump` - Select trump suit
- POST `/api/games/{id}/rounds/current/play-decision` - Decide to play round
- POST `/api/games/{id}/rounds/current/exchange-cards` - Exchange cards
- POST `/api/games/{id}/rounds/current/play-card` - Play a card
- GET `/api/games/{id}/state` - Get current game state
- GET `/api/games/{id}/scores` - Get score history

### User Profile
- GET `/api/users/{id}` - Get user profile
- PUT `/api/users/{id}` - Update profile
- GET `/api/users/{id}/statistics` - Get game statistics

## gRPC Services (game-events.proto)

```protobuf
service GameEvents {
  // Subscribe to game events
  rpc Subscribe(SubscribeRequest) returns (stream GameEvent);

  // Send player action
  rpc SendAction(PlayerAction) returns (ActionResponse);
}

message GameEvent {
  string game_id = 1;
  EventType type = 2;
  google.protobuf.Timestamp timestamp = 3;

  oneof payload {
    PlayerJoined player_joined = 10;
    GameStarted game_started = 11;
    TrumpSelected trump_selected = 12;
    CardDealt card_dealt = 13;
    CardPlayed card_played = 14;
    TrickCompleted trick_completed = 15;
    RoundCompleted round_completed = 16;
    GameCompleted game_completed = 17;
  }
}
```

## Error Response Standard
```json
{
  "error": {
    "code": "INVALID_CARD_PLAY",
    "message": "You must follow suit when possible",
    "details": {
      "requiredSuit": "Hearts",
      "playedCard": "5_Clubs"
    },
    "timestamp": "2026-02-02T12:00:00Z"
  }
}
```

## Acceptance Criteria
- OpenAPI spec is complete and validates
- All endpoints documented with examples
- gRPC proto files compile successfully
- Error responses are standardized
- API documentation is auto-generated
- Postman collection can be imported and used

